            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sweet potato fries are cooking, combine your <strong>lean pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!), <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide the pork mixture and shape into 2 oval patties per person</p><p>Pop them in the fridge until later</p>",
