      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>sliced shallot </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and grind to a paste</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> – this is your <strong>spicy sambal</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Use a food processor instead!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1690888450244-x200.jpg",
