      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the patties are cooking, chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>in a bowl with the juice of the <strong>remaining lime </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> raita-style dressing</strong></p>",
