    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Sri-Lankan-style lean pork patties</strong> with the <strong>sweet potato fries</strong>, <strong>raita-style slaw </strong>and <strong>spicy sambal </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
